      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:98px;\"><a href=\"http://www.logos.ic.i.u-tokyo.ac.jp/~tsuruoka/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/6/6f/Tsuruoka.jpg\" width=\"96\" height=\"120\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Tsuruoka.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Yoshimasa Tsuruoka <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</b>,<br />\na Japanese computer scientist, <a href=\"/Shogi\" title=\"Shogi\">Shogi</a> programmer and associate professor at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Tokyo\">University of Tokyo</a> and before at <i>School of Information Science</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> , <a href=\"/JAIST\" title=\"JAIST\">Japan Advanced Institute of Science and Technology (JAIST)</a>. His research topics include <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natural_language_processing\">natural language processing</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Text_mining\">text mining</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Biomedical_engineering\">biomedical</a> literature, <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">artificial intelligence</a> in <a href=\"/Games\" title=\"Games\">games</a>, and <a href=\"/Deep_Learning\" title=\"Deep Learning\">deep learning</a>. Yoshimasa Tsuruoka is co-author of the Shogi engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gekisashi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gekisashi (page does not exist)\">Gekisashi</a>, Gold medal winner of the <a href=\"/15th_Computer_Olympiad#Shogi\" title=\"15th Computer Olympiad\">15th Computer Olympiad, Shogi</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kanazawa,_Ishikawa\">Kanazawa</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yoshimasa_Tsuruoka&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yoshimasa_Tsuruoka&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a>, <a href=\"/Daisaku_Yokoyama\" title=\"Daisaku Yokoyama\">Daisaku Yokoyama</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Chikayama\" title=\"Takashi Chikayama\">Takashi Chikayama</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.2.9258\">Game-Tree Search Algorithm based on Realization Probability</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 3</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Daisaku_Yokoyama\" title=\"Daisaku Yokoyama\">Daisaku Yokoyama</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Maruyama\" title=\"Takashi Maruyama\">Takashi Maruyama</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Chikayama\" title=\"Takashi Chikayama\">Takashi Chikayama</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sciencelinks.jp/j-east/article/200218/000020021802A0583583.php\">Implementation of \"Gekisashi\". A Computer Shogi Player</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sciencelinks.jp/j-east/journal/J/L0461A/2006.php\">Joho Shori Gakkai Natsu no Puroguramingu, Shinpojiumu Hokokushu</a> (Japanese)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yoshimasa_Tsuruoka&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Nobuo_Araki\" title=\"Nobuo Araki\">Nobuo Araki</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Kazuhiro_Yoshida&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Kazuhiro Yoshida (page does not exist)\">Kazuhiro Yoshida</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jun&#39;ichi_Tsujii\">Jun'ichi Tsujii</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i>Move Prediction in Go with the Maximum Entropy Method</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cswww.essex.ac.uk/cig/2007/index.jsp?page=papers.html\">CIG 2007</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cswww.essex.ac.uk/cig/2007/papers/2070.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>Recent Advances in Computer Shogi and Gekisashi</i>. IPSJ Magazine, Vol. 49, No 8 (Japanese)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yoshimasa_Tsuruoka&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Gekisashi wins Shogi Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#33_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 33, No. 4</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/15th_Computer_Olympiad#Nurikabe\" title=\"15th Computer Olympiad\">15th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Akira_Ura\" title=\"Akira Ura\">Akira Ura</a>, <a href=\"/Makoto_Miwa\" title=\"Makoto Miwa\">Makoto Miwa</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Chikayama\" title=\"Takashi Chikayama\">Takashi Chikayama</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-319-09165-5_18\">Comparison Training of Shogi Evaluation Functions with Self-Generated Training Positions and Moves</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_2013\" title=\"CG 2013\">CG 2013</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/6ad0/7167425539cf64e6bf420d7a28a1fc1047d6.pdf\">slides as pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Kunihito_Hoki\" title=\"Kunihito Hoki\">Kunihito Hoki</a>, <a href=\"/Tomoyuki_Kaneko\" title=\"Tomoyuki Kaneko\">Tomoyuki Kaneko</a>, <a href=\"/Daisaku_Yokoyama\" title=\"Daisaku Yokoyama\">Daisaku Yokoyama</a>, <a href=\"/Takuya_Obata\" title=\"Takuya Obata\">Takuya Obata</a>, <a href=\"/Hiroshi_Yamashita\" title=\"Hiroshi Yamashita\">Hiroshi Yamashita</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a>, <a href=\"/Takeshi_Ito\" title=\"Takeshi Ito\">Takeshi Ito</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/6598505/\">A System-Design Outline of the Distributed-Shogi-System Akara 2010</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/snpd/snpd2013.html\">SNPD 2013</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yoshimasa_Tsuruoka&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Yun-Ching_Liu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Yun-Ching Liu (page does not exist)\">Yun-Ching Liu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i>Adapting Improved Upper Confidence Bounds for Monte-Carlo Tree Search</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_14\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 14\">Advances in Computer Games 14</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Akira_Ura\" title=\"Akira Ura\">Akira Ura</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Chikayama\" title=\"Takashi Chikayama\">Takashi Chikayama</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/ipsjjip/23/1/23_9/_article\">Dynamic Prediction of Minimal Trees in Large-Scale Parallel Game Tree Search</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/browse/ipsjjip/\">Journal of Information Processing</a>, Vol. 23, No. 1</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Naoki_Mizukami\" title=\"Naoki Mizukami\">Naoki Mizukami</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i>Building a Computer Mahjong Player Based on Monte Carlo Simulation and Opponent Models</i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TOCIAIGAMES\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE CIG 2015</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.logos.ic.i.u-tokyo.ac.jp/~mizukami/paper/cig_2015.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Naoki_Mizukami\" title=\"Naoki Mizukami\">Naoki Mizukami</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jun_Suzuki&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jun Suzuki (page does not exist)\">Jun Suzuki</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Hirotaka_Kameko&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Hirotaka Kameko (page does not exist)\">Hirotaka Kameko</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Exploration Bonuses Based on Upper Confidence Bounds for Sparse Reward Games</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_15\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 15\">Advances in Computer Games 15</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Hirotaka_Kameko&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Hirotaka Kameko (page does not exist)\">Hirotaka Kameko</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jun_Suzuki&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jun Suzuki (page does not exist)\">Jun Suzuki</a>, <a href=\"/Naoki_Mizukami\" title=\"Naoki Mizukami\">Naoki Mizukami</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Deep Reinforcement Learning with Hidden Layers on Future States</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCA2017\" title=\"Conferences\">Computer Games Workshop at IJCAI 2017</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lamsade.dauphine.fr/~cazenave/cgw2017/Kameko.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Keigo_Kawamura&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Keigo Kawamura (page does not exist)\">Keigo Kawamura</a>, <a href=\"/Naoki_Mizukami\" title=\"Naoki Mizukami\">Naoki Mizukami</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Neural Fictitious Self-Play in Imperfect Information Games with Many Players</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCA2017\" title=\"Conferences\">Computer Games Workshop at IJCAI 2017</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lamsade.dauphine.fr/~cazenave/cgw2017/Kawamura.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yoshimasa_Tsuruoka&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.logos.ic.i.u-tokyo.ac.jp/~tsuruoka/\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka - University of Tokyo</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=691\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.nactem.ac.uk/tsuruoka/maxent/\">A simple C++ library</a> for <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Principle_of_maximum_entropy\">maximum entropy</a> classification</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yoshimasa_Tsuruoka&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.logos.ic.i.u-tokyo.ac.jp/~tsuruoka/\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.jaist.ac.jp/is/index.php\">JAIST School of Information Science</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#RefDB\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Reference Database</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.logos.ic.i.u-tokyo.ac.jp/~tsuruoka/publications.htm\">Publications</a> of <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/David_Levy\" title=\"David Levy\">David Levy</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ilk.uvt.nl/icga/journal/contents/content25-3.htm#SOME%20COMMENTS%20ON%20REALIZATION%20PROBABILITIES\">Some Comments on Realization Probabilities and the SEX Algorithm</a></i>.<a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 3</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20